  "prompt": "Which earphones are better under 2000?",
  "response": "When choosing earphones under 2000 INR, several models stand out due to their sound quality, durability, and features. Here are some of the top picks you might consider:\n\n1. **Realme Buds Wireless 2 Neo**: \n   - Features: Magnetic earbuds, IPX4 water resistance, 17-hour battery life.\n   - Sound: Good bass and clear sound quality.\n\n2. **boAt Rockerz 255 Pro+**: \n   - Features: Bluetooth v5.0, IPX7 water resistance, 40-hour playback time.\n   - Sound: Known for deep bass and good audio clarity.\n\n3. **OnePlus Bullets Wireless Z Bass Edition**: \n   - Features: Warp Charge (10 minutes for 10 hours), magnetic control, quick switch.\n   - Sound: Enhanced bass and balanced sound profile.\n\n4. **JBL C100TWS True Wireless Earbuds**:\n   - Features: Truly wireless, up to 17 hours of combined playback, JBL Pure Bass sound.\n   - Sound: Good for bass lovers with clear vocals.\n\n5. **Soundcore Life U2 by Anker**:\n   - Features: 24-hour playtime, IPX7 waterproof, fast charging.\n   - Sound: Deep bass and high clarity.\n\n6. **Sony WI-C200**: \n   - Features: Bluetooth v5.0, 15-hour battery life, quick charge.\n   - Sound: Clean and crisp sound with decent bass.\n\n7. **Boult Audio AirBass PowerBuds**: \n   - Features: True wireless, IPX7 waterproof, 18-hour playback.\n   - Sound: Heavy bass and wide soundstage.\n\nWhen choosing earphones, consider your priorities such as battery life, waterproofing, voice assistant integration, or specific sound preferences like bass-heavy or balanced audio. Personal comfort and design preference also play a crucial role, so it might be beneficial to try them out physically if possible.",
